name: BonsorBadminton
skdetail:

Invocation Name: badminton courses
des: A simple helper to check the available courses in Burnaby Bonsor Complex, you can say 'check 10 am on Sunday' or 'check Sunday' to check available courses on Sunday after the time you specified. You can also say 'available' to check the earliest available courses.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
